{"tid":568350,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"嶺南係咪剩系好過OU少少","createTime":"2018-02-21T16:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T16:27:14.000Z","uid":166815,"like":6,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"962afe4ce386ceb0468b1bd2282b75b5485dda80","tid":568350,"uid":166815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:53:39.000Z","msg":"話說嶺南係屯門，系<strong>郊區，</strong>唔似OU得<strong>一棟野</strong>系<strong>市區</strong>都可以早過佢升格叫「大學」<br />\n<br />\nOU雖然科科都<strong>無ranking</strong>，又唔似嶺南商學院甘有AACSB，<strong>但勝在無限開科</strong>，有Nursing，嶺南得三個學院<br />\n<br />\nOU雖然<strong>年滿十七歲即可入讀</strong>，但勝在有<strong>全日制每人有三萭+不定期的funding補助，可以無限擴</strong>招，有無限資助學額，同嶺南學額限住限住甘唔同<br />\n<br />\nOU雖然好似每年<strong>得一二個人入Big 4</strong>，但勝在每年出200個倒的「會計師」，同巨量(mental health) nurses <strong>你搵唔工 </strong>再同你講<strong>無包生仔</strong><br />\n<br />\nOU雖然年滿十七歲即可入讀，但勝在<strong>資歷架構第五級</strong>，可以好神奇甘<strong>二年入面</strong>(Ordinary degree)由小學畢業train 到佢變<strong>大學生</strong>，<strong>成本效益不脛而出</strong><br />\n<br />\n嶺南人衰係英文差，IELTS<strong>八大入面</strong><strong>排尾2(包尾)</strong>，但OU人係<strong>八大之外</strong>，勝在<strong>無考的需要</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ef0f70fb1439dc74fa57cfe337ec16f0feca62","tid":568350,"uid":36077,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"b3661dfc9a9ad2ea9f4132eed1d6f037cae66e95","tid":568350,"uid":38904,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KKZAq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKKZAq.gif&h=6e7a45b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e0aa99a248a938ee2965a7fa5b5b20a100c9c4a","tid":568350,"uid":47857,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"開大First Hon&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;嶺大"},{"pid":"5a162b499c64f92b7c0a054b59b85b13aab0400b